HEADWORD: Hesperian
<hw>Hes*pe"ri*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>hesperius</ets>, fr. <ets>hesperus</ets> the evening star, Gr. <?/
