==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Hesperian
<hw>Hes*pe"ri*an</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A native or an inhabitant of a
western country.</def> <mark>[Poetic]</mark> <rj><au>J.
Barlow.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

