==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Hesperian
<hw>Hes*pe"ri*an</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Of or
pertaining to a family of butterflies called <fam>Hesperidae</fam>, or
skippers.</def> -- <def2><pos>n.</pos> <def>Any one of the numerous
species of <fam>Hesperidae</fam>; a skipper.</def></def2>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Hesperid</ent>⟦br⟧
